    {
      "id": "1954750c-f3ba-809a-8e51-f36c42e36a81",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The paper presents open-ended Knowledge Tracing. They lay out the specifications and evaluation metrics and conduct experiments to test the open-ended knowledge tracing on a real world dataset. ",
